      "text": [
        " اَلصَّادِقُ عَلَيْهِ اَلسَّلاَمُ : «قَضَاءُ حَاجَةِ اَلْمُؤْمِنِ أَفْضَلُ مِنْ طَوَافٍ وَ طَوَافٍ وَ طَوَافٍ حَتَّى عَدَّ عَشْراً »."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.2159 - Imam Jafar ibn Muhammad Al-Sadiq (as) said: \"Fulfilling the need of a believer is better than performing Tawaf, and Tawaf, and Tawaf—up to ten times.\""
        ]
